  "body": "Affects only group chats. Have not reproduced in community channels. \r\n\r\n**Preconditions:** Users A and B are mutual contacts and members of the same group. \r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n1. User A generates group notifications for User B: sends couple of replies, couple of mentions. As a result User B observes mentions/replies notifications in AC. \r\n2. Do not read unread group messages by User B\r\n3. User A deletes for everyone one of the messages containing mention of User B\r\n4. Wait until message will be deleted\r\n5. Open AC by User B and see if rest of  unread group notifications are still there\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** AC is empty, all unread notifications disappeared. \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** only notification for deleted message should disappear. The rest of unread notifications should remain in AC. \r\n\r\n[User_A.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/files/10559742/User_A.zip)\r\n[User_B.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/files/10559743/User_B.zip)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/216117964-11b52216-ca55-4b8e-a01d-cf164bfb2d27.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
